snippet.title: Sonic & SEGA All-Stars Racing - Banjo-Kazooie & Avatars Join The Race
snippet.description: Exclusively for XBox 360, Rare's Bear and Bird combination bring their racer, the Bolt Bucket to take on Sonic, Ryo, Billy Hatcher and SEGA's best... AND YOU. Yes, your avatar can join the fun in the "Avacar" and your All-Star move? Well... we get by with a little help from our friends....
